==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From [[μέσος]] {{GG|3319}} and [[ποταμός]]  {{GG|4215}}

===Pronunciation===
*Μεσοποταμία / Mesopotamia / mes-op-ot-am-ee'-ah

===Proper noun===
'''Μεσοποταμία'''

# Mesopotamia (as lying between the Euphrates and the Tigris; compare [[ארם נהרים]] {{HH|763}}), a region of Asia: - [[Mesopotamia]].

